Package: ALccdfDB
Type: Package
Title: Alabama CCDF Administrative Data Cleaning and Management
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("JoonHo", "Lee",
           email = "jlee296@ua.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-4019-8703"))
Description: A modular toolkit for cleaning, validating, linking, and managing
    Alabama CCDF (Child Care and Development Fund) administrative records from
    the Alabama Department of Human Resources (DHR). Features data-driven column
    mapping for heterogeneous Excel report formats, purpose-built cross-module
    linkage with diagnostics, Melissa.com geocoding integration (lat/lng,
    census tract, FIPS), proper factor levels for categorical variables,
    DuckDB-based persistent storage, and multiple export formats (CSV, Excel,
    Stata, Parquet, RDS).
